## 2. Restricted Uses (Commercial License Required)

The following uses **require a paid Commercial License** obtained from the
author before deployment:

- Integration into a commercial product (SaaS / desktop / mobile / embedded)
  sold for revenue, or distributed as part of a paid bundle
- Operating a paid service built on Praditor ("VAD-as-a-service", hosted voice-activity-detection
  API access, audio boundary detection processing for fee)
- Use by organizations with revenue >= USD $1M/year OR headcount >= 10,
  internally
- Re-distribution into any paid package, paid installer, or commercial
  container image
- Use in client work performed for compensation (consulting / hourly / fixed-
  fee work where the deliverable incorporates Praditor)

