## 3. Commercial Licensing

> **Contact**: open an issue on GitHub tagged `commercial-license`, or message
> GitHub user `Paradeluxe`.
> GitHub user `Paradeluxe`.

Commercial licenses typically include:
- Unlimited commercial use of the current and prior 12 months of versions
- All minor + patch releases for 6 months from purchase
- Priority GitHub issue response (within 24 hours)
- One-time fee, **amount negotiated by company size and use case** (typical
  range for small-to-medium businesses: US$ 200–5,000)

Reply window: 7 business days.

